flowchart LR
    A[Sem fragmento] --> B[append 1]
    B --> C[reflow]
    C --> D[append 2]

    D --> E[reflow]
    E --> F[... 98 vezes mais]
    F --> G[100 reflows]
    H[Com fragmento] --> I[append 100 no fragmento]
    I --> J[0 reflows]
    J --> K[append fragmento na arvore]
    K --> L[1 unico reflow]